" XVim
" https://github.com/JugglerShu/XVim/blob/master/Documents/Users/FeatureList.md

set noincsearch
set smartcase

nmap <C-j> <Esc>
vmap <C-j> <Esc>
imap <C-j> <Esc>
omap <C-j> <Esc>


nmap ,,  :write<cr>
imap ,,  <Esc>:write<cr>


" ビジュアルモード時vで行末まで選択
vmap v $

" like screen
vmap <space> y

nmap 0 ^

